4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/Th%E1%BB%8B-y%E1%BA%BFn/poem-z7guycCGz02MA5Ik49qVkg">Thị yến - 侍宴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/author-eVhiQaGgvOZuXB8qH633Iw">Thẩm Thuyên Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-L%E1%BB%85/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-sn8Iwv-S1-0eXxgMIS72Cw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-L%E1%BB%85/author-Wr0M9A9cS_PDVlFSGIsm6Q">Tông Lễ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Tr%E1%BA%A5n-Nam-Quan/poem--cwIimn8ufdouXrN49NYRg">Trấn Nam Quan - 鎮南關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C3%82m-d%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1t/poem-WBlRALx57Yzq5dcby2KL7w">Tương Âm dạ phát - 湘陰夜發</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
